Class DefaultIndexedGraph<N extends IndexedNode<N>>

    public class DefaultIndexedGraph<N extends IndexedNode<N>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IndexedGraph<N>
    The default implementation of a graph for the IndexedAStarPathFinder that uses an internal Array to store nodes.
